<title>USA: PC Quote says President Meltzer resigns.</title>
<headline>PC Quote says President Meltzer resigns.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-07-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>PC Quote Inc said Monday that Howard Meltzer has resigned as president and chief operating officer of the company to pursue other interests.</p>
<p>The resignation is effective immediately.</p>
<p>PC Quote provides on-line stock and market quotes in real-time and delayed to financial professionals, consumers and redistributors.  </p>
<p>PC Quote does not plan to fill the position at the present time, the company said in a news release.</p>
<p>Jim Porter, who was recently named PC Quote's chief executive officer, will assume Meltzer's responsibilities.</p>
<p>Shares of PC Quote were trading off 2/16 to 2-1/16.</p>
